{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-mateo/task-5","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-meet-mateo","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mateo spominje svoj uzrast na španskom koristeći sledeću strukturu, i glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tener</span> (\"imati\"):</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo</span> + broj rečima + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">años</span>.</p>\n<p>Napomena, španske brojeve od 21 do 29 počinju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinti-</span>, praćenim odgovarajućim brojem. Primer:</p>\n<p>25 je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinticinco</span>. Ovo nastaje uklanjanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span> i dodavanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> pre broja <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od 1 do 9 na španskom su:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Španski Izraz</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">nueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Usemi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo veinticinco años</span> znači da je Mateo star 25 godina.</p>\n<p>Zapamti da slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ñ</span> u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">años</span> ima drugačiji zvuk.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk/audio i odgovori na pitanje koje je ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-mateo/task-5"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koliko godina ima Mateo?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco años</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovaj broj ne odgovara uzrastu koji je Mateo spomenuo.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinte años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovaj uzrast je manji od onoga što je Mateo rekao.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiocho años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovaj broj zvuči kao taj, ali to nije onaj pravi koji je Mateo rekao.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Mateo","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_meet_mateo.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":7.65,"finishTimestamp":9.27},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.62,"dialogue":{"text":"Tengo veinticinco años